name: Fruit of the Spirit Jingles MP3
description:
Each "fruit" of the Spirit is cross-referenced with scriptures and set to catchy tunes that will definitely hide the word of God in the hearts of children and parents alike. These jingles are great for teaching lessons at home or in a classroom setting.

MP3 Only

name: Little Songbirds Physical CD
description:
Now available! Rachel & Wallace Faagutu's brand new Kids' Praise & Worship album. But it's not only for kids, adults will absolutely enjoy this! It's a wonderful album from top to bottom, and the excellence on every song shines through. 

This album has funny and catchy tunes like "Egypt Exodus Song" that will make you laugh while learning about the 10 plagues, island-style jams like "Going Up to the House", "God is Good", "I Was Made to Worship", & so much more. And there's the sweet ballads of worship in "Jesus Is Worthy" and "Near To Me". It's the most unique kid/adult worship album ever made. 

From mixing and mastering, to instrument solos and arrangements, this album is excellent and engaging. And to top it off, it's highly anointed!

IMPORTANT NOTICE: We are currently back-ordered. Orders will begin shipping on October 14, 2013.
